# SRM Electronic Health Records (EHR) System

A modern, role-based Electronic Health Records (EHR) web application built with Streamlit and MySQL. This system provides dedicated portals for patients, doctors, and hospital administrators, enabling functionalities such as appointment scheduling, health report management, prescription tracking, and more.îˆ†

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- **Role-Based Access Control**:îˆƒSeparate dashboards for Admin, Doctor, and Patient rolesîˆ„îˆ†
- **User Authentication**:îˆƒSecure login and signup processes with password reset functionalityîˆ„îˆ†
- **Appointment Management**:îˆƒPatients can book appointments; doctors can view and manage their schedulesîˆ„îˆ†
- **Medical Reports**:îˆƒUpload and view medical reports securelyîˆ„îˆ†
- **Prescription Handling**:îˆƒDoctors can add prescriptions; patients can view their prescribed medicationsîˆ„îˆ†
- **Chatbot Assistance**:îˆƒIntegrated chatbot to assist users with common queriesîˆ„îˆ†
- **Admin Controls**:îˆƒManage users, view system analytics, and oversee overall operationsîˆ„îˆ†

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Frontend** îˆƒ[Streamlit](https://streamlit.io)îˆ„îˆ†
- **Backend** îˆƒPythnîˆ„îˆ†
- **Database** îˆƒMySLîˆ„îˆ†
